com.plexus.sam.net
Class FTPTransferModule

java.lang.Object
  com.plexus.sam.net.FTPTransferModule
All Implemented Interfaces:
FileTransferModule
public class FTPTransferModule
extends java.lang.Object
implements FileTransferModule

Implementation of the FileTransfer facade interface for the FTP protocol. All information is gathered from the ftp configuration group, including a remote base path from which relative file/directory requests can be made.

Following settings are used:

  • remote_path : location on the server
  • connect_mode : ACTIVE or PASSIVE
  • control_port : should be a valid integer
  • hostname : i.e. ftp.someserver.com
  • user_id : username of the ftp account
  • password : password of the ftp account
  • transfer_type : BINARY or ASCII
  • server_type : WIN or UNIX
  • server_locale : i.e. en_US

Author:
plexus
